Package: speciesmap
Type: Package
Title: Species Occurrences And Climate Observations
Version: 0.3-3
Imports:
    sp,
    stringr,
    ALA4R,
    rgbif,
    raster,
    futile.logger
Maintainer: Remko Duursma <remkoduursma@gmail.com>
Description: Retrieve species occurrences from GBIF or ALA, and retrieve climate
    variables at the occurrences from WorldClim and the CGIAR-CSI aridity database. 
    Optionally rasterize occurrences at resolution of Worldclim to reduce sampling bias.
License: GPL-2
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/RemkoDuursma/speciesmap
BugReports: https://github.com/RemkoDuursma/speciesmap/issues
